    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_WONDER_THEOPETRACAVE_HELP">
      <Text>+1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold from Stone Resource worked by the City it is built in. Also provides +1 Food [ICON_FOOD].</Text>
